name: Patina Earrings, Mustard Glass Red Patina Brass - Beadwoven Earrings - Sunflowers in Yellow
description:
- Mustard Yellow bead-woven Brass filigree medallions, heat patinaed in a deep, rich Red. These are woven, one tiny glass seed bead at a time, with waxed nylon thread. They hang from handmade Raw Brass round hook ear wires.
These have been sealed securely in lacquer and then rubbed with preservation wax, before weaving, for added durability. Still, I recommend removing these before bathing/swimming.

- Measure: 1-1/2" (3.8cm) in length.

name: Mustard Aqua Sienna Patina Brass - Beadwoven Earrings -Boho Chic
description:
- Brass filigree medallions, heat patinaed in rich Sienna. Bead-woven with Mustard Yellow, Aqua Turquoise and White glass seed beads and faceted rounds. They hang from simple Sterling Silver french hook ear wires.
These have been sealed securely in lacquer and then rubbed with preservation wax, before weaving, for added durability. Still, I recommend removing these before bathing/swimming.

- Measure: 1-3/8" (3.5cm) in length.

name: Blue Red Patinaed Brass Triangle Riveted - Earrings
description:
- Dark, Denim Blue and Deep Red heat patinaed Brass triangles, stacked and riveted with raw Copper studs. Hung from shiny Copper french hook earwires.
Each piece has been sealed securely in lacquer and then rubbed with preservation wax for added durability. Still, I recommend removing these before bathing/swimming.

- Measure: 1-5/8" (4cm) in length.

name: Sea Blue, Rustic Brown Brass Dangle - Patina Earrings - Boho Chic
description:
- Lightly textured Brass rounds heat-patinaed in Sea Blue, paired with thin, long Brass ovals, heat patinaed in Rustic Brown. Hung from Brass french hook ear wires. This patina has been heat applied, left to cure, then sealed securely in lacquer and rubbed with preservation wax for added durability.
Still, I recommend removing these before bathing/swimming.

- Measure: 2-3/8" (6cm) in length.

name: Blue Patina Brass Tubing, Poppy Orange - Beadwoven Necklace -Roam No.1
description:
- Hand patinaed Dark Blue curved Brass tubing, embellished with a strip of peyote stitched beadwoven seed beads in Poppy Orange. It is strung on Antiqued Brass cable link chain and is finished with a simple Brass trigger clasp.
This piece has been sealed securely in lacquer and then rubbed with preservation wax for added durability. Still, I recommend removing before bathing/swimming.

- Measures: 17" (43cm) in length.
